OL,4,BVAR: Referees are in sheer panic at
OL,5,Bvideo decisions, says Chris Sutton
OL,6, Premier League referees are in "sheer
OL,7, panic" at how the video assistant
OL,8, referee system is being used, says
OL,9, former Chelsea striker Chris Sutton.
OL,11,FThe league has brought in VAR this
OL,12,Fseason to decide on goals, penalties,
OL,13,Fred cards and offside decisions.
OL,15,FBut a number of high-profile incidents
OL,16,Fhave been criticised, as has the length
OL,17,Fof time before a verdict is given.
OL,19,FSutton said: "I was a fan of VAR but
OL,20,Fshould we take the subjective calls out
OL,21,Fof it?"
